HEADWORD: Cloud-capped
<hw>Cloud"-capped`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having clouds
resting on the top or head; reaching to the clouds; <as>as,
<ex>cloud-capped</ex> mountains</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

